amesmarket

Class DefaultSimulationParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • amesmarket.DefaultSimulationParameters

  • public class DefaultSimulationParameters
extends java.lang.Object
    Default simulation parameters. A struct-type class to group the default parameters together to make it easy to pass them around. Public visibility to make is simpler to hook into existing code. TODO: Can remove the final modifier on parameters if needed. TODO: Make this a "static final" type constant declaration class? Adapted from the AMESFrame
